The architects saw one - a kindergarten also belongs to the office
The Avriopoint office building in Brno is the new headquarters of the company Arch.Design
But who would expect a mini-kindergarten here, with everything that goes with it: brightly colored walls, creative furniture, a lot of toys, and even a mini-playground on the outdoor terrace.
This kindergarten has been available to Arch.Design staff members since last year.
